群星灿烂 海洋汹涌 大地沉默.Translation: The stars shine brightly, the ocean surges, the earth is silent.

一切有序如常 与昨日并无区别.Translation: Everything is orderly as usual, no different from yesterday.

旅途还未结束....Translation: The journey is not yet over...

走廊还有30秒可以通行.Translation: The corridor is passable for another 30 seconds.

走廊还有20秒可以通行.Translation: The corridor is passable for another 20 seconds.

走廊还有10秒可以通行.Translation: The corridor is passable for another 10 seconds.

走廊已开放，??还需要坚持10秒.Translation: The corridor is open, but we still need to hold for 10 seconds.

世界在旋转 你的思绪却陷入凝固.Translation: The world is spinning, but your thoughts are frozen.

尽管已经察觉到了不协调的地方.Translation: Although you have noticed the discordant elements.

但你面对困苦与疲惫而无暇寻找.Translation: But you are too overwhelmed by hardship and fatigue to search.

但愿它只是狂风呼啸之下微不足道的隐患....Translation: Hopefully, it is just a trivial hazard beneath the howling winds...

它们从大地的深处向上攀爬.Translation: They are climbing up from the depths of the earth.

它们缓慢地从土壤中渗透出来.Translation: They are slowly seeping out from the soil.

它们一直在试图改变你，试图将你变为它们的一部分…….Translation: They have been trying to change you, trying to make you a part of them...

如今，它们又将向你耳语....Translation: Now, they will whisper to you again...

往后 世界的一切都将永恒统一 不复改变....Translation: From now on, everything in the world will be eternally unified and no longer change...

大地在流淌 群星向下腾升.Translation: The earth flows, and the stars ascend.

你听到...潮湿的泥土之中有生物向上坠落的声音.Translation: You hear... the sound of creatures falling upwards from the damp soil.

但它并非没有尽头....Translation: But it is not without an end...

大海凝固了 群星也不再运动.Translation: The ocean has solidified, and the stars no longer move.

就连语言与光线也停滞在空中.Translation: Even language and light are suspended in the air.

你知道...这就是你想要的.Translation: You know... this is what you wanted.

群星...灿烂 海洋..汹涌 大地.沉默.Translation: Stars... shining brightly, the ocean... surging, the earth... silent.

一切有序如常... 与昨日并无区别别别....Translation: Everything is orderly as usual... no different from yesterday...

旅途还未结束...无法结束....Translation: The journey is not yet over... cannot end...

办公室还有5秒传送.Translation: 5 seconds left for the office transmission.

还有10秒！有什么东西要下来了....Translation: 10 seconds left! Something is coming down...

他们将这里称为那些幽灵缅怀过去的场所，它们临时的故乡.Translation: They call this place a site where ghosts reminisce about the past, their temporary homeland.

这里只有永不停歇的冷风在呼啸，只有绝无落下可能的悬日或者永恒慈悲的夜幕.Translation: Here, only the ceaseless cold wind howls, with no possibility of the sun setting or the eternal mercy of the nightfall.

灵魂回归了摇篮，时代开始倒退，一切的一切被拉扯着回到事物最开始的起点.Translation: Souls return to the cradle, time begins to reverse, and everything is pulled back to the very beginning of things.
